      <title>隨著格魯吉亞對峙加劇，億萬富翁前總理重返舞台</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/billionaire-ex-pm-returns-stage-georgian-standoff-intensifies-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一位隱居的億萬富翁創始人的推動下，格魯吉亞執政黨引發了與年輕的反莫斯科抗議者的對峙，這場對峙日益緊張和暴力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/billionaire-ex-pm-returns-stage-georgian-standoff-intensifies-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 15:51:19 GMT</pubDate>
